just Muffin now?

01:53.043 --> 01:55.115
Yeah, my new steeze
is a little Lauren,

01:55.115 --> 01:56.392
a lil Lil Muffin.

01:56.392 --> 01:58.842
Same flavor,
just more baked.
Baked, I heard that.

01:58.842 --> 02:00.327
Okay, now I got
to ask y'all --

02:00.327 --> 02:03.951
