05:13.727 --> 05:15.315
Because I'm a woman
and I'm not white.

05:15.315 --> 05:16.730
Good point.

05:16.730 --> 05:18.766
Afraid to ask,
but where's this coming from?

05:18.766 --> 05:22.839
Trying to write this song
about you, but it's not...

05:22.839 --> 05:24.082
